        <abstract> 
<p>Much interested in WCR’s paper on "Whirlwinds excited by fire" [<hi rend="italic">Am. J. Sci.</hi> 36 (1839): 50–9; <hi rend="italic">Edinburgh New Philos. J.</hi> 27 (1839): 369–79].</p>  
<p>Sends a summary account of circular clouds and waterspouts formed during volcanic eruption in the Azores [S. Tillard, "Eruption of a volcano in sea off St Michael", <hi rend="italic">Philos. Trans. R. Soc. Lond.</hi> (1812): 152–8].</p> 
        </abstract>
